org.pipservices.runtime

Interface ICache

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCache, MemoryCache, NullCache

    public interface ICache
extends IComponent
    Transient cache which is used to bypass persistence to increase overall system performance.
    Since:
    2016-05-01
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Sergey Seroukhov

    • Method Detail

      • retrieve

        Object retrieve(String key)
        Retrieves a value from the cache by unique key. It is recommended to use either string GUIDs like '123456789abc' or unique natural keys prefixed with the functional group like 'pip-services-storage:block-123'.
        Parameters:
        key - a unique key to locate value in the cache
        Returns:
        a cached value or null if value wasn't found or timeout expired.

      • store

        Object store(String key,
             Object value)
        Stores value identified by unique key in the cache. Stale timeout is configured in the component options.
        Parameters:
        key - a unique key to locate value in the cache.
        value - a value to store.
        Returns:
        a cached value stored in the cache.

      • remove

        void remove(String key)
        Removes value stored in the cache.
        Parameters:
        key - a unique key to locate value in the cache.
